{"tid":696241,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣最美的風景...","createTime":"2018-06-10T02:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T17:56:00.000Z","uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49c9e7d493603a0fb588b06754b33b875525a85a","tid":696241,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"小毒依加身在台灣 發現周街都係台妹 個個熱褲短T露淫腳露滑肚 見到想即刻狗衝去奶乾淨哂佢地身上既每日滴汗液<br />\n樣又清純過香港個班垃撚圾閪面女人 又識嗲 日日揸機車載佢都可以D奶波餅吃到飽<br />\n試問啲男人困係台灣日日被逼望呢啲野 谷撚到無時無刻都流緊前列腺液 真係難怪台灣風化案咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最撚可悲既係見親啲正既台妹身邊都拖住個臭肥宅 個個都below金鐘樣 而香港就靚仔配美極<br />\n到底台灣呢個地方發生咩事阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：搭緊高鐵隔離有個白滑長腿靚樣，好想認識佢今晚大戰300回合 將我既優良種子散播全台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80e3ac264ca13f8de1bea505987120da42f06f1","tid":696241,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2878f2fe69e541a7a9e231608c34f29023f7d2b","tid":696241,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"c341e76de73ad25b98e20555363dfdb51d51c06a","tid":696241,"uid":7583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"講咁多野咪又係自己打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadafb34fe0de5855adea24580c5e528afb70686","tid":696241,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"十九歲人就打少啲飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927e20c3671d023492fd3726b71870db6f38ce3a","tid":696241,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"是淫"},{"pid":"62c2bbcee84cff19b90c1c74f1257885